# ✅ **3. PlantUML (Sequence Diagram)**

👉 Simple, consistent with your other diagrams, includes `CcaLedger`

```plantuml
@startuml
actor User
participant Ui
participant CcaLedger
participant Parser
participant AddEventCommand
participant CcaManager
participant EventManager

User -> Ui: enter "add-event Hackathon ComputingClub 2026-04-01"
Ui -> CcaLedger: input

CcaLedger -> Parser: parse(input)
Parser -> AddEventCommand: new AddEventCommand(...)

CcaLedger -> AddEventCommand: execute(...)

AddEventCommand -> CcaManager: getCCAList()
AddEventCommand -> CcaManager: find CCA by name

alt CCA exists
    AddEventCommand -> EventManager: addEvent(eventName, cca, dateTime)
    AddEventCommand -> Ui: showMessage(...)
else CCA not found
    AddEventCommand -> Ui: showError(...)
end
@enduml